Day 8

Topic       :  SR Latch

Truth Table :


S  | R  | Q(t) | Q(t+1)
---|----|------|-------
0  | 0  | Q(t) | Q(t)
0  | 1  | Q(t) | 0
1  | 0  | Q(t) | 1
1  | 1  | -    | -


In this truth table:

S is the set input.
R is the reset input.
Q(t) represents the current state of the output.
Q(t+1) represents the next state of the output.